Package net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.postprocess.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractJsChainedResourceBundlePostProcessor
    This class defines the abstract JS postprocessor
    CssCharsetFilterPostProcessor
    This class defines the Css Bundle Charset cleaner.
    CSSCombineMediaPostProcessor
    This class defines the post processor which combines style sheets for different media types into a single file, surrounding them with a @media block.
    CSSImportPostProcessor
    This class defines the Post processor which handle the inclusion of the CSS define with @import statement
    CSSMinPostProcessor
    Performs minification on CSS files by removing newlines, expendable whitespace and comments.
    CSSURLPathRewriterPostProcessor
    Single file postprocessor used to rewrite CSS URLs according to the new relative locations of the references when added to a bundle.
    CustomJsPostProcessorChainWrapper
    Wrapper class for custom JS user made postprocessors.
    CustomPostProcessorChainWrapper
    Wrapper class for custom user made postprocessors.
    JSMinPostProcessor
    This postprocessor will minify a javascript bundle using Douglas Crockford's JSMin, in its java implementation (see www.crockford.com and www.inconspicuous.org).
    LicensesIncluderPostProcessor
    Meant to be used after compression, this postprocessor will include the license comments that may be desired to send with each bundle, including those required by open source licenses.
    PostProcessorCssImageUrlRewriter
    This class defines the URL rewriter for the Css post processor
